        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">hey all </P><P>mobs are too boring. they can all be thwacked with some sort of stick and have varying degrees of magic resistance. grab a tank and a cleric and you are in business.</P><P>this is too lame.</P><P>we need :-</P><P>mobs that ALWAYS enrage tearing the tanks to pieces. dinosaurs would be kinda like this. </P><P>mobs with big natural (undispellable) damage shields.</P><P>mobs covered in indestructible scaly armour that can only be hit with piercing weapons (can anyone say dragon?)</P><P>iron golems that are actually iron so theres no point belting them with your sword</P><P>goos with no back to stab</P><P>mobs that try to absorb the munk so feign pulling is a death wish</P><P>mobs that hit for not very much but really really fast tearing thru a melee in short order but with not many hp</P><P>to balance this out make them very susceptible to different types of magic. get all those neglected casters hanging around to nuke/aoe/dot in a frenzy to take the mobs down.</P><P>boss mobs are getting stupid. like that one in the hole with a 2000pt lifetap proc every 2 seconds. or a totally MR cazic. or mobs that quad for 1000 and have 250000hp</P><P>verant has the shits with players for beating their game. its because they can all be beaten the same way. throw a pile of tanks with healage and support casting and you are in business. the only way for them to make this tactic NOT succeed is to up the mobs hp/damage output and then start adding nifty little quirks like aoe silence or DT's every 5 seconds. and still the players win.</P><P>change tack fellas. you have been worked out. stubbornly bashing your head against the player base will get you nowhere.</P><P>i would love to see a dragon raid where hitting it's 2000 year old scaly gem encrusted hide does very little, where a rogue can only backstab its tail defeating the purpose, where it is highly resistant to cold OR fire OR diease or something leaving the player to figure out WHICH resist classes to bring along.</P><P>dragon can't be belted or nuked? better scrounge a few necros and shaman to poison and disease the mofo then and worry about keeping those worthless lag causing tanks alive.</P><P>a change beats the hell out of a holiday</P><P>feel free to add other mob type ideas. i can stick it all in a post to the developers corner for them to ignore later <img src=icon_smile_tongue.gif border=0 align=middle></P><P>dead people make the best friends</P><P></P><P>Edited by - Morlock on 06/12/2001  05:46:01</font></td>
